### Log Analysis
- Search for OOMKilled events, "OutOfMemoryError", or "disk space exhausted" in **{{ service_name }}** logs.
- Look for GC log patterns indicating heap pressure.
- Check system logs for disk I/O errors or filesystem issues.
{% endif %}

