- Check node conditions: `kubectl describe nodes | grep -A5 Conditions`
- Check pod resource usage: `kubectl top pods -l app={{ service_name }}`
- Review resource requests/limits: `kubectl get pods -l app={{ service_name }} -o yaml | grep -A4 resources`
- Check for evicted or pending pods due to resource constraints.
{% endif %}

